<pb ed="T" id="T55.2164.1071c" n="1071c"/>
<lb n="1071c01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="1071c02"/><head type="no">No. 2164</head>
<lb n="1071c03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="1"/><note n="1071046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】鎌倉時代寫高山寺藏本，【甲】享保二年寫大谷大學藏本，【乙】大日本佛教全書，【丙】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本</note><jhead>靈巖<note n="1071047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔寺〕－【丙】</note><app n="1071047"><lem>寺</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="1071048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（和尚…等））九字＝（（圓行和尚））四字【甲】【丙】</note><app n="1071048" word-count="9"><lem>和尚請來法門道具等</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">圓行和尚</rdg></app>
<lb n="1071c04"/>目錄</jhead></juan>
<lb n="1071c05"/>
<lb n="1071c06"/><div1 type="xu"><mulu type="序" level="1" label="上表"/><p>入唐還學沙門<note n="1071049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔圓行言〕－【甲】</note><app n="1071049"><lem>圓行言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。圓行載次戊午。銜命
<lb n="1071c07"/>請益之列。訪道西海之外。其年臘月得到長
<lb n="1071c08"/>安<note n="1071050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔城〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071050"><lem>城</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。歲次己未正月十<note n="1071051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝二&M062403;【原】</note><app n="1071051"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">二</rdg></app>日。依奏奉&CB00330;住
<lb n="1071c09"/>青龍寺。幸遇彼寺灌頂教主法<note n="1071052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">號＝蹄【丙】</note><app n="1071052"><lem>號</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">蹄</rdg></app>義真和尚
<lb n="1071c10"/>以為師主。其大<note n="1071053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔威〕－【甲】【丙】</note><app n="1071053"><lem>威</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>德則惠果阿闍梨弟子同
<lb n="1071c11"/>門義操和尚付法之弟子也。明閑<note n="1071054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝二【丙】</note><app n="1071054"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg></app>教。妙通
<lb n="1071c12"/>五部。法之<note n="1071055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">棟梁＝所歸【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071055"><lem>棟梁</lem><rdg wit="【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">所歸</rdg></app>。國之所<note n="1071056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔歸〕&M062403;－【乙】，歸＝師【丙】</note><app n="1071056"><lem>歸</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【乙】">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">師</rdg></app>圓行幸賴聖朝
<lb n="1071c13"/>之鴻恩。師主之深慈。決疑兩部之大法。開悟
<lb n="1071c14"/>諸尊之密法。閏正月二日蒙授阿闍梨位灌
<lb n="1071c15"/>頂也。左街功德使并僧錄和尚供奉大德金
<lb n="1071c16"/>剛門<note n="1071057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">徒＝從【丙】</note><app n="1071057"><lem>徒</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">從</rdg></app>悉集道場共致隨喜。斯法也觀心月
<lb n="1071c17"/>輪則居住凡位<note n="1071058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">備＝脩【丙】</note><app n="1071058"><lem>備</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">脩</rdg></app>佛陀之德。誦口密言則不
<lb n="1071c18"/>逕長劫頓登<note n="1071059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝天【乙】</note><app n="1071059"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">天</rdg></app>覺之位。故龍樹<note n="1071060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔言〕－【乙】</note><app n="1071060"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。乘羊而
<lb n="1071c19"/>行。<note n="1071061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">願＝顯【乙】，頓&M062485;【乙】</note><note n="1071061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">願＝顯【乙】，＝頓&M062485;【乙】</note><app n="1071061"><lem><sic corr="頓" resp="【乙】">願</sic></lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">顯</rdg></app><note n="1071062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">難＋（難）【乙】</note><app n="1071062"><lem>難</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">難難</rdg></app>致遠策馬而馳漸期差疾。乘神通
<lb n="1071c20"/>行發念則到。是則顯密之別<note n="1071063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">也＝色【乙】</note><app n="1071063"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">色</rdg></app>。亦祕密經
<lb n="1071c21"/>言。一善男子建立道場修念三密。其國界內
<lb n="1071c22"/>無七難災。國<note n="1071064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＝主【甲】</note><app n="1071064"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">主</rdg></app>大臣<note n="1071065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">日日＝月日【丙】</note><app n="1071065"><lem>日日</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">月日</rdg></app>增長福壽。是則
<pb ed="T" id="T55.2164.1072a" n="1072a"/>
<lb n="1072a01"/>真言之功矣。雖然波浪沷漢。風雨漂舶。越彼
<lb n="1072a02"/>鯨海平歸聖境。是則聖力之所能也。伏惟皇
<lb n="1072a03"/>帝陛下功超<note n="1072001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">玄＝立【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1072001"><lem>玄</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】" resp="Taisho">立</rdg></app>極道<note n="1072002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">冠＝&CB00018;【甲】</note><app n="1072002"><lem>冠</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00018;</rdg></app>混<note n="1072003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">元＝無【丙】</note><app n="1072003"><lem>元</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">無</rdg></app>。讚堯寶圖。復
<lb n="1072a04"/>禹<note n="1072004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">丕續＝丕績【甲】【丙】，不請【乙】</note><note n="1072004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">丕續＝丕績【甲】【丙】，＝不請【乙】</note><app n="1072004"><lem>丕續</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">丕績</rdg><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">不請</rdg></app>。悲蒼生而濡足。鍾佛囑而<note n="1072005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">垂＝乘【丙】</note><app n="1072005"><lem>垂</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">乘</rdg></app>衣。以
<lb n="1072a05"/>陛下興隆佛法。沒馱之舍利浸波遠來。以陛
<lb n="1072a06"/>下慈育海內。祕密之經法過海遙到也。祕法
<lb n="1072a07"/>傳來非<note n="1072006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝只【甲】，是＋（足）【丙】</note><app n="1072006"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">只</rdg><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">是足</rdg></app>無以也。如來本有福智之力。法界
<lb n="1072a08"/>本性加持之力矣。大日如來。金剛薩埵。龍猛
<lb n="1072a09"/>菩薩。龍智菩薩。金<note n="1072007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">剛＋（智）【丙】</note><app n="1072007"><lem>剛</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">剛智</rdg></app>三藏。不空三藏。惠果
<lb n="1072a10"/>和尚。義操和尚。義真和尚。次第相傳。即授圓
<lb n="1072a11"/>行。所授經法舍利道具等目錄在別。謹以奉
<lb n="1072a12"/>進輕黷威嚴伏增戰越。沙門圓行誠恐誠惶
<lb n="1072a13"/>謹言。</p>
<lb n="1072a14"/><p rend="margin-left:2em">承和六年十二月十九日入唐還學沙門
<lb n="1072a15"/>傳燈大法師位圓行上表</p></div1>
<lb n="1072a16"/><div1 type="other"><mulu type="其他" level="1" label="入唐沙門圓行承和六年請來經佛道具目錄"/><head>入唐沙門圓行承和六年請來經佛道<note n="1072008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">具＋（等）【丙】</note><app n="1072008"><lem>具</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">具等</rdg></app>目
<lb n="1072a17"/>錄</head>
<lb n="1072a18"/><p>都<note n="1072009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（合）&M062403;【乙】</note><app n="1072009"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【乙】">合合</rdg></app><note n="1072010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">七＝十【乙】</note><app n="1072010"><lem>七</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">十</rdg></app>種。</p>
<lb n="1072a19"/><list><item><note n="1072011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（新請…卷）十六字∞（梵字…卷）六字【甲】</note><note n="1072011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（新請來真言經法都二十六部三十三卷）十六字∞（梵字三部四卷）六字【甲】</note><app n="1072011"><lem>新請來真言經法。<note n="1072012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">都＋（合）【甲】【丙】</note><app n="1072012"><lem>都</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">都合</rdg></app>二十六部三十三卷</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">梵字三部四卷</rdg></app></item>
<lb n="1072a20"/><item><note n="1072013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（新請…卷）十六字∞（梵字…卷）六字【甲】</note><note n="1072013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（新請來真言經法都二十六部三十三卷）十六字∞（梵字三部四卷）六字【甲】</note><app n="1072013"><lem>梵字三部四卷</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">新請來真言經法都二十六部三十三卷</rdg></app></item>
<lb n="1072a21"/><item>顯教經論疏章等。都四十部八十八卷
<lb n="1072a22"/><p rend="margin-left:2em">已上三種。總六十九部一百二十<note n="1072014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝五【丙】</note><app n="1072014"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">五</rdg></app>卷。</p></item>
<lb n="1072a23"/><item>佛舍利都三千餘粒</item>
<lb n="1072a24"/><item>付屬物三種</item>
<lb n="1072a25"/><item>佛像曼荼<note n="1072015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔羅〕－【丙】</note><app n="1072015"><lem>羅</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>圖樣都十二種</item>
<lb n="1072a26"/><item>道具都十六箇</item></list></div1>
<lb n="1072a27"/><div1 type="other"><mulu type="其他" level="1" label="新請來真言經法"/><head>新請來真言經法</head>
<lb n="1072a28"/><list><item><title>奇特最勝金輪佛頂念儀軌一卷</title></item>
<lb n="1072a29"/><item><title>白傘蓋佛頂儀軌一卷</title></item>
<pb ed="T" id="T55.2164.1072b" n="1072b"/>
<lb n="1072b01"/><item><title>一字頂輪王念誦儀軌一卷</title><note place="inline">依忉利天王宮會所說經譯</note></item>
<lb n="1072b02"/><item><title>蘇悉地法</title>一部二卷</item>
<lb n="1072b03"/><item><title>諸佛境界<note n="1072016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">攝＝樣【甲】</note><app n="1072016"><lem>攝</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">樣</rdg></app>真實經</title>一部三卷<note place="inline">般若三藏譯</note></item>
<lb n="1072b04"/><item><title>降三世儀軌一卷</title><note place="inline">遍智阿闍梨指授</note></item>
<lb n="1072b05"/><item><title>與金剛弟子入壇受灌頂法經一卷</title></item>
<lb n="1072b06"/><item><title>金剛吉祥大成就品經<note n="1072017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一卷〕－【乙】</note><app n="1072017"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></title><note place="inline">亦名五眼經出金剛頂峰經</note></item>
<lb n="1072b07"/><item><title>念誦結護法普通諸</title>部一卷</item>
<lb n="1072b08"/><item><title>最上乘受菩提心戒及心地祕決一卷</title><note place="inline">三藏善無畏依<note n="1072018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（祕）&M062403;＋密【乙】</note><app n="1072018"><lem>密</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【乙】">祕密</rdg></app>
<lb n="1072b09"/>教出弟子一行記</note></item>
