<lb n="1073c08"/><item><title>率都波鈴一　商佉螺一</title>
<lb n="1073c09"/><p rend="margin-left:2em">右件傳法阿闍梨執持供養修行三昧耶
<lb n="1073c10"/>也。</p>
<lb n="1073c11"/><p>以前經法道具舍利顯教經論疏章等請來如
<lb n="1073c12"/>件。<note n="1073048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔但雖…焉〕四十七字－【乙】</note><app n="1073048" word-count="47"><lem>但雖真言宗一百二十<note n="1073049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三〕－【甲】</note><app n="1073049"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>部祕法儀軌
<lb n="1073c13"/>等子細勘<note n="1073050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">校＝授【丙】</note><app n="1073050"><lem>校</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">授</rdg></app>請來。先入唐大師空海阿闍梨
<lb n="1073c14"/>延曆年中請來已<note n="1073051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">了＝畢【丙】</note><app n="1073051"><lem>了</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">畢</rdg></app>。仍更不載目錄焉</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="1073c15"/><p rend="margin-left:2em">承和六年十二月十九日。</p>
<lb n="1073c16"/><p rend="margin-left:4em">入唐沙門傳燈大法<note n="1073052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">師＋（位）【甲】【丙】</note><app n="1073052"><lem>師</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【丙】" resp="Taisho">師位</rdg></app>圓行<note place="inline">上</note>。</p>
<lb n="1073c17"/><p><note n="1073053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以下高山寺本無之今依甲本補載以乙丙二本對校之</note>右街僧錄三教講論大德沙門體<note n="1073054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">虛＝處【丙】</note><app n="1073054"><lem>虛</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">處</rdg></app>。奉本
<lb n="1073c18"/>使<note n="1073055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">仇＝仉【丙】</note><app n="1073055"><lem>仇</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">仉</rdg></app>驃騎<note n="1073056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怗＝帖差【丙】</note><app n="1073056"><lem>怗</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">帖差</rdg></app>三覺供奉大德六人就青龍寺
<lb n="1073c19"/>與日本國傳燈大法師位圓行語論本教玄理
<lb n="1073c20"/>具名如後。</p>
<lb n="1073c21"/><p rend="margin-left:3em">保壽寺內供奉臨壇大德沙門常辨。</p>
<lb n="1073c22"/><p rend="margin-left:3em">章敬寺內供奉禪宗大德沙門<note n="1073057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">弘＝和【丙】</note><app n="1073057"><lem>弘</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">和</rdg></app>辨。</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T55.2164.1074a" n="1074a"/>
<lb n="1074a01"/><p rend="margin-left:3em">招福寺內供奉講論大德沙門齊<note n="1074001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">高＝亮【丙】</note><app n="1074001"><lem>高</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">亮</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="1074a02"/><p rend="margin-left:3em">興唐寺內供奉講論大德沙門<note n="1074002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">光顥＝先顯【丙】</note><app n="1074002"><lem>光顥</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">先顯</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="1074a03"/><p rend="margin-left:3em">雲花寺內供奉講論大德沙門海岸。</p>
<lb n="1074a04"/><p rend="margin-left:3em">青龍寺內供奉講論大德沙門圓鏡。</p>
<lb n="1074a05"/><p>右件大德等所與圓行大德語論教門策目並
<lb n="1074a06"/>錄申<note n="1074003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聞＝問【丙】</note><app n="1074003"><lem>聞</lem><rdg wit="【丙】" resp="Taisho">問</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="1074a07"/><p rend="margin-left:2em">開成四年正月十五日。</p></item></list></div1>
